GET {{ClipOrganizer.Api_HostAddress}}/api/tags
Accept: {{ContentType}}

### Get tag categories
GET {{ClipOrganizer.Api_HostAddress}}/api/tags/categories
Accept: {{ContentType}}

### Create a new tag
POST {{ClipOrganizer.Api_HostAddress}}/api/tags
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}

{
  "category": "SkillTactic",
  "value": "Flick"
}

### Create tag - Field Area example
POST {{ClipOrganizer.Api_HostAddress}}/api/tags
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}

{
  "category": "FieldArea",
  "value": "Attacking D"
}

### Create tag - Player Role example
POST {{ClipOrganizer.Api_HostAddress}}/api/tags
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}

{
  "category": "PlayerRole",
  "value": "Goalie"
}

### Create tag - Outcome/Quality example
POST {{ClipOrganizer.Api_HostAddress}}/api/tags
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}

{
  "category": "OutcomeQuality",
  "value": "Success"
}

